assert self.table.keys() == ['key-2', 'key-1']
items = [{self.table_key: 'key-3', 'answer-1': 42}, {self.table_key:
    'key-4', 'answer-1': 42}]
self.table.add_batch(items)
keys = self.table.keys(use_cache=False)
assert len(keys) == 4
assert 'key-3' in keys
items = [{self.table_key: 'key-3'}, {self.table_key: 'key-4'}]
self.table.delete_batch(items)
keys = self.table.keys()
assert len(keys) == 4
